page.title: 19Employment continued
page.content: 3.Premier Footwear -manufacture of slipper uppers -32 employees. 4.F.D.Curwen -car body repairs -3 employees. 5.Fit-rite -wrought-iron gates,railings,etc -15 employees. 6.Jas Woods -pre-cast concrete products -5 employees. 7.Preesall Garage -car sales,petrol,retail,car repairs and maintenance -12 employees. 8.Farms -mostly dairy -at least 80. 9.Hotels,Public House and Restaurants -at least 30. 10.Shops(various) -at least 30 11.Schools -at least 10 12.Council Depot -about 10 13.Rest Homes -about 20 We intended giving also a list of clubs and societies,but suffice it to say there are many of all types.
